    "This self-awareness enables models to provide more accurate and reliable predictions while also identifying when they may be out of their depth.",
    "This research path is crucial for LLMs in sensitive domains such as healthcare, finance, and autonomous vehicles, where the consequences of incorrect results can be severe.",
    "Rise of Sparse Expert Models:Sparse expert models represent a departure from the traditional approach of large, dense neural networks.",
    "Instead of relying on massive numbers of parameters, sparse expert models focus on a select set of specialized neurons or modules that excel at specific tasks.",
    "This approach is inspired by the human brain, where different regions specialize in different cognitive functions."
